data.description: This Open and Airy Bi Level located in the Mountain View Section of sought after Bear Creek Lakes Community is situated on over an ACRE! Main level boasts of open concept living space with vaulted ceilings and provides ample natural light through sky lights. Wonderful Home for entertaining with Spacious Kitchen w/ black stainless steel appliance, granite countertop and Dining area which leads to a 3 Season room. Main level offers Main Bedroom w/ En-Suite, 2 additional bedrooms & full bathroom. Lower level has a large Recreation room with Wood Stove and Glass Sliders leading to rear yard. In addition there is a 4th Bedroom/Home Office. Laundry area located in the Full Bath on Lower level. Rear yard offers Fenced area which is ideal for pets or gardening. Paved driveway which leads to one car garage. Minutes to historical town of Jim Thorpe.
